'''南海爭端'''指[[南海|南海]]周边的幾個國家因為對於該海域的部分島嶼的主權归属、海域划分和相关海洋权利的聲索產生重疊從而發生的衝突。涉及該爭端的國家和地区有[[中華民國|中華民國]]（台湾）、[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]（中国大陆）、[[越南|越南]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[汶萊|汶萊]]、[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]。

南海領土爭端包括[[南沙群島主權爭議|南沙群島]]、[[西沙群島|西沙群島]]和[[中沙群島|中沙群島]]的主權糾紛和海域糾紛<ref>{{cite news |last=Keck |first=Zachary |date=20 March 2014 |title=China’s Newest Maritime Dispute |url=http://thediplomat.com/2014/03/chinas-newest-maritime-dispute/ |newspaper=The Diplomat |access-date=12 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228151534/http://thediplomat.com/2014/03/chinas-newest-maritime-dispute/ |dead-url=no }}<br />{{cite news |last=Vaswani |first=Karishma |date=19 October 2014 |title=The sleepy island Indonesia is guarding from China |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-29655874 |newspaper= |location= |access-date=19 October 2014 |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223202953/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-29655874 |dead-url=no }}<br />{{cite news |last=R.C. Marshall |first=Andrew |date=25 August 2014 |title=Remote, gas-rich islands on Indonesia's South China Sea frontline |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/25/us-southchinasea-indonesia-natuna-insigh-idUSKBN0GP1WA20140825 |newspaper=Reuters |access-date=12 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203750/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/25/us-southchinasea-indonesia-natuna-insigh-idUSKBN0GP1WA20140825 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。由於南海的漁業資源、原油和天然氣蘊藏皆十分豐富，同時南海作為重要的航運通道，戰略地位重要，沿海各個國家出於自身利益，希望控制自己所主張擁有主權的部分島嶼及其專屬經濟區。<ref name="ICSMaritimeSecurity">{{cite book|date=2021|title=Maritime Security - A comprehensive Guide for Shipowners, Seafarers and Administrations|location=Livingston|publisher=[[Witherby_Publishing_Group|Witherby Publishing Group]] and the [[International_Chamber_of_Shipping|International Chamber of Shipping]]|page=13|isbn=9781913997014}}</ref>

南海問題已有多年紛爭，曾多次在區域內爆發軍事衝突，而作為現代重要的航運通道及地緣政治的考慮，越來越受到國際社會的關注，2016年的[[南海仲裁案|南海仲裁案]]更是一列。

為減少衝突，[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]和[[東盟|東盟]]10國於2002年11月4日在[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]][[金邊|金邊]]簽署[[南海各方行為宣言|南海各方行為宣言]]，作為各國在南海活動的準則。[[香格里拉對話|香格里拉對話]]是相關國家為解决該地區爭端和衝突的一個重要平臺<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.iiss.org/en/events/shangri%20la%20dialogue/archive/shangri-la-dialogue-2015-862b/opening-remarks-and-keynote-address-6729/keynote-address-a51f |title = Keynote Address: Lee Hsien Loong |publisher =  |accessdate = 30 July 2015 |archive-date = 2017-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170303120638/http://www.iiss.org/en/events/shangri%20la%20dialogue/archive/shangri-la-dialogue-2015-862b/opening-remarks-and-keynote-address-6729/keynote-address-a51f |dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{Link-en|亞太安全合作理事會|Council for Security Cooperation in the Asia Pacific}}則是各國間為協調亞太地區的安全問題的另外一個重要平臺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cscap.org/uploads/docs/CRSO/CRSO2014.pdf |title=Regional Security Outlook 2014 |work=CSCAP |accessdate=26 November 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923211436/http://www.cscap.org/uploads/docs/CRSO/CRSO2014.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cscap.org/uploads/docs/CRSO/CSCAPCRSO2015.pdf |title=Regional Security Outlook |work=CSCAP |accessdate=26 November 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923211442/http://www.cscap.org/uploads/docs/CRSO/CSCAPCRSO2015.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

